WEBVTT

00:04:28.230 --> 00:04:30.536
they had to live in complete darkness,

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:33.932
unable to tolerate
the sound of a human voice

00:04:33.956 --> 00:04:35.865
or the touch of a loved one.

00:04:37.469 --> 00:04:41.471
I was diagnosed
with myalgic encephalomyelitis.

00:04:42.554 --> 00:04:46.006
You've probably heard it called
"chronic fatigue syndrome."

00:04:46.987 --> 00:04:48.909
For decades, that's a name

00:04:48.933 --> 00:04:50.538
that's meant that this

00:04:51.578 --> 00:04:52.961
has been the dominant image

00:04:52.985 --> 00:04:56.260
of a disease that can be
as serious as this.

00:04:57.468 --> 00:04:58.992
The key symptom we all share

00:04:59.016 --> 00:05:02.768
is that whenever we exert ourselves --
